<scene id="00" title="Wedge" root="true">
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>In the endless darkness, [\s]the dead Celestial's consciousness awakened.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-01白光转场"></se>
  <delay t="0.15"></delay>
  <transition in="1" stop="0.5" out="1.5" color="#ffffff" mode="fade"></transition>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>In the beginning, the new consciousness was like the birth of the world:[\s]</p>
    <p>just a spot of light in the universe.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-01恢复意识" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <bg img="BGIntel1" duration="3"></bg>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>『Its』power was still limited. [\s] It can neither receive signals from the senses, nor send them to the nerves.</p>
  </mono>
  <bg img="BGIntel3" duration="5"></bg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>In that chaos, the weak consciousness followed its ancient instincts.[\s]</p>
    <p>Blindly but firmly, it awakened and started growing.</p>
  </mono>
  <delay t="0.2"></delay>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>It has not realized its own death yet.[\s]</p>
    <p>The girl refuses to acknowledge her own death.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-01恢复意识" looptimes="0"></se>
  <transition in="2" stop="0" out="0" color="#ffffff" mode="dissolve"></transition>
  <transition mode="fade" in="0" stop="0.2" out="1.5" color="#FFFFFF"></transition>
  <bg img="PureBlack"></bg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Judging by common sense, the immortal Celestial is indeed dead.</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢碎片1"></cg>
  <delay t="0.5"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>Her right leg has been cut off, and it's missing from the ankle below.</mono>
  <event action="hide_ui"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢碎片2"></cg>
  <delay t="0.5"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>Her hands are crippled.</mono>
  <event action="hide_ui"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢碎片3"></cg>
  <delay t="0.5"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>All her internal organs are destroyed.</mono>
  <event action="hide_ui"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢碎片4"></cg>
  <delay t="0.5"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>Her chest has taken more than a dozen blows.</p>
  </mono>
  <cg duration="0.5"></cg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>However, the deadliest wound is on her head.</p>
  </mono>
  <transition in="0.6" stop="0" out="0" color="#8b0000" mode="dissolve"></transition>
  <transition mode="fade" in="0" stop="0.2" out="0.15" color="#8b0000"></transition>
  <se id="01-02大剑命中"></se>
  <motion chara="-4" action="shake" duration="0.1" range="80" direction="horizontal"></motion>
  <bg img="BGBlood1"></bg>
  <mono>It was wounded by a sword.</mono>
  <mono inline="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>The sword struck her forehead,</p>
  </mono>
  <mono inline="true"> destroyed her brain,</mono>
  <mono> and passed through to the back of her head.</mono>
  <mono>If it were for any other person, they would have died with just one of those injuries.</mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>But the「Celestial」wasn't ordinary.</p>
  </mono>
  <transition mode="eye" in="2" stop="0" out="2" color="#000000"></transition>
  <se id="01-03野外小屋loop" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡" duration="0" origin="15%,0%" scale="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2.2"></delay>
  <bg></bg>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono pageend="true">The Celestial is an immortal being that never died.</mono>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>
    <p>Her body wouldn't die even after thousands of years,[\s]</p>
    <p>neither would her soul, even after tens of thousands of years.[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>She completely overthrew the laws of nature,[\s]</p>
    <p>she was the one and only Celestial of Shenzhou.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>This was the very essence of the body that was now lying still in the stone chamber.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono>And so,</mono>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <se id="01-03野外小屋loop" looptimes="0"></se>
  <se id="01-04痊愈loop" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡" duration="8" scale="1" origin="15%,0%"></cg>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>starting from each braincell,[\s]</p>
    <p>the Celestial's mind and body began a long period of repair and reconstruction.</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <delay t="7"></delay>
  <mono pageend="true">Drawing on every breath from her surroundings,</mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="2"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡2" duration="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <se id="01-05痊愈"></se>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>patching up the torn skin,</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="2"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡3" duration="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <se id="01-06痊愈"></se>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>healing the broken bones,</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="2"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡4" duration="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <se id="01-07痊愈"></se>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>tying up the crumbling muscles,</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="2"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡5" duration="2"></cg>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <se id="01-05痊愈"></se>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>repairing the damaged organs……</p>
  </mono>
  <delay t="2"></delay>
  <transition in="3" stop="0.5" out="0" color="#ffffff" mode="halo"></transition>
  <se id="01-04痊愈loop" looptimes="0"></se>
  <cg></cg>
  <transition in="0" stop="0" out="1" color="#ffffff" mode="fade"></transition>
  <bgm id="千年之羽"></bgm>
  <bg img="PureBlack"></bg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Gradually, the Celestial's 『consciousness』started perceiving its surroundings.</p>
  </mono>
  <transition mode="move" in="1" stop="0.5" out="0.5" color="#000000" direction="left" custom="thick"></transition>
  <letterbox action="show_letterbox" height="400" duration="0"></letterbox>
  <se id="01-03野外小屋loop" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <bg img="BGSky00"></bg>
  <mono>She saw the line of light and shadow going from east to west and from west to east through the little window of the chamber.</mono>
  <letterbox action="show_letterbox" height="300" duration="1"></letterbox>
  <bg img="BGSky01"></bg>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>She could smell the odor of the withering plants mixing with rotting insects.</p>
  </mono>
  <letterbox action="show_letterbox" height="200" duration="1"></letterbox>
  <bg img="BGSky02"></bg>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>She heard the sound of falling leaves, welcoming the autumn, and the snow-covered branches swaying.</p>
  </mono>
  <letterbox action="show_letterbox" duration="1" height="100"></letterbox>
  <bg img="BGSky04"></bg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p>Then, she felt pain,[\s] numbness,[\s] swelling,[\s] itching……[\s] every part of her body was screaming.[\s]</p>
    <p>An endless torment took her over……</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-03野外小屋loop" looptimes="0"></se>
  <letterbox action="hide_letterbox" duration="0"></letterbox>
  <bg img="PureBlack" duration="3"></bg>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>……an endless recovery,[\s] an endless pain.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>The Celestial remains silent.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-08扰乱心神杂音loop" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <bg img="BGNeuron03" duration="3"></bg>
  <mono chara="000" pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「     Who         am         I         ?      」</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>Her mind is still confused. [\s]</p>
    <p>She remembers some things but forgets more and more.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono chara="000" pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「     Where         is         this         ?      」</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>With just fragments in her memory, she can't put together the answer she seeks.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono chara="000" pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「     ……          wh-          ?      」</p>
  </mono>
  <bgm id="千年之羽" looptimes="0"></bgm>
  <se id="01-08扰乱心神杂音loop" looptimes="0"></se>
  <transition mode="fade" in="1" stop="0.5" out="1" color="#000000"></transition>
  <bgm id="余烬"></bgm>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡end"></cg>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Suddenly[\s]</p>
    <p>thinking of that made long abandoned emotions swell up in her chest.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-09心跳loop" looptimes="-1"></se>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="0.5"></event>
  <motion action="shake" chara="-4" range="30" direction="default" duration="0.1" delay="0.1"></motion>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>Seven……</p>
  </mono>
  <delay t="0.2"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>The Seven people closest to her.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p>The Seven Swords that stayed by her side for the longest time.</p>
  </mono>
  <motion chara="-4" action="shake" duration="0.1" range="30" direction="default" looptimes="1"></motion>
  <mono pageend="true" inline="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>Seven people that conspired, lured her to doom.[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Seven Swords that trapped her and killed her.</p>
  </mono>
  <se id="01-09心跳loop" looptimes="0"></se>
  <transition mode="dissolve" in="1" stop="0.5" out="1" color="#000000"></transition>
  <bg img="PureBlack"></bg>
  <cg></cg>
  <mono chara="000" pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「       ……              Why         ?      」</p>
  </mono>
  <transition mode="fade" in="1" stop="0.5" out="1" color="#000000"></transition>
  <bg img="BGNeuron01"></bg>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢沉睡end"></cg>
  <mono pageend="true" inline="true">
    <p>Many emotions swelled up endlessly:[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>anger,[\s]</p>
    <p>doubt,[\s]</p>
    <p>resentment,[\s]</p>
    <p>fury,[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>and sadness, at the end.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono chara="000">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>「 ……why? 」</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>There's no answer, only the desire to find one.</p>
  </mono>
  <event action="hide_ui" duration="3"></event>
  <cg img="CG_第一折_赤鸢苏醒end" duration="3"></cg>
  <delay t="3"></delay>
  <event action="show_ui"></event>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>……the Celestial decided to wait.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>She has protected this land for countless years.[\s]</p>
    <p>Time doesn't matter for her anymore.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true" inline="true">
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>She will keep waiting until her body and mind are fully healed,[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>then she will find those Seven[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>and ask them why they killed her.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono>
    <p>A strong desire was branded deep into her consciousness,[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>urging her,[\s]</p>
    <p>pushing her,[\s]</p>
    <p>changing her.[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>The wait becomes a habit[\s]</p>
    <p>and the pain becomes natural.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p></p>
    <p>And then……</p>
  </mono>
  <transition mode="clock" in="2" stop="0.5" out="0" color="#000000"></transition>
  <transition mode="fade" in="0" stop="0" out="2" color="#000000"></transition>
  <cg></cg>
  <mono>
    <p>Pain[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>       Pain[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>              Pain[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>                     Pain[\s]</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Endless recovery and endless pain.</p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p>The Celestial remains silent.</p>
  </mono>
  <transition in="1" stop="0.1" out="1" color="#000000" mode="dissolve"></transition>
  <bg img="PureBlack"></bg>
  <mono>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p></p>
    <p>She has endured for a long time,</p>
    <p></p>
  </mono>
  <mono pageend="true">
    <p>she can still endure it.</p>
  </mono>
  <bgm looptimes="0"></bgm>
  <event action="hide_ui"></event>
  <transition in="1" stop="0.5" out="1" color="#000000" mode="fade"></transition>
  <bg img="Chapter01"></bg>
  <delay t="2.5"></delay>
  <se id="01-10标题试剑"></se>
  <delay t="6"></delay>
  <transition in="2" stop="3" out="0" color="#000000" mode="fade"></transition>
  <event action="goto" to="01"></event>
</scene>
